      "text": [
        "۴۰۳. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): مَنْ أَوْمَأَ إِلَى مُتَفَاوِتٍ خَذَلَتْهُ الْحِيَلُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "403. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: Whoever hankers after contraries gets no means of success."
